{"tid":1007242,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"發現同好朋友距離好遠","createTime":"2019-02-03T15:36:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T10:54:12.000Z","uid":163911,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1cb2f87fc21d0a54268a79671b04afbd2668da84","tid":1007242,"uid":163911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:36:17.000Z","msg":"由初中識到出黎做野，<br />\n初初個個都好單純，宜家個個都好現實，<br />\n見佢地識既男朋友個個都要有私樓，<br />\n所有既洗費都唔洗自己比，<br />\n想要既野都係叫人買，<br />\n打份廢工就月月清，淨係唸去邊度吃學玩樂。<br />\n書又讀唔好，又唔好好增值自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唉，我唔知點講<br />\n就算友誼都已經唔係咁純潔，<br />\n我覺得自己同佢地世界好唔一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3327630b8ba004579c7d5723c65a4a258107acac","tid":1007242,"uid":77569,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8abd3f5c6f73bd3f79d22c5825a9e187de64a937","tid":1007242,"uid":163911,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"3327630b8ba004579c7d5723c65a4a258107acac","tid":1007242,"uid":77569,"like":8,"dislike":8,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:38:28.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"祝你搵到d識玩既<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b2f89183375f3403412ba6d90c81cda2d0de6e2","tid":1007242,"uid":76603,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:42:39.000Z","msg":"請問閣下又有幾成功呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11be7a4115cb9d417892c5ba194282c0e4ab8005","tid":1007242,"uid":167808,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:44:39.000Z","msg":"同樓主觀值觀好似 有時心諗點解要為自己set d咁hardcore既遊戲規則 學似人地咁無咁多心理枷鎖日子會過得輕鬆好多 但同一時間知道自己做唔到佢地 唔會過到自己果關"},{"pid":"1c93a3712ea00efc56ad86e929569444c5686663","tid":1007242,"uid":163911,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"8b2f89183375f3403412ba6d90c81cda2d0de6e2","tid":1007242,"uid":76603,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"